== Overview ==

'''[[Gamma Sector]]''' (commonly called '''Gamma''') is the third and most advanced outland zone in Cybots — the endgame frontier beyond the [[Talsian Warfront]]. If Vulcore taught you how to play Cybots, and Talsia taught you how to fight it, then Gamma is where everything you've learned gets stress-tested at once. It is deliberately non-linear, deeply quest-driven, and designed so that '''no two Controllers will take the same path through it.'''

This guide is a walkthrough and strategy companion. General information about Gamma — its factions, traders, chassis, quests, and reward mechanics — lives on the main [[Gamma Sector]] page. This guide focuses on ''how to approach'' Gamma: patrol sequencing, squad setups, priorities, and what to watch out for.

{{Quote|Gamma was designed to take the boredom out of having a squad that cannot die and one-click everything until the end of the set. Being invincible is not as rewarding as having to work your way around scared — knowing you will get blasted on a misclick or ambush.|maximo0727, lead developer}}

{{Quote|Gamma is more open-ended. You need to change dynamically. You will die in Gamma. The most important thing is how you think about your goals.}}

