[[File:Cybulwark.jpg|thumb|right|200px|[[CyBulwark]] — Arena Champion and centrepiece of the Carnutum Ignus Arena fights.]]

The '''Carnutum Ignus Arena''' (also called the Lava Arena) in the SW quadrant is Gamma's equivalent of Talsia's [[Master Controllers]]. Defeating the Arena Masters awards the '''[[Hydroplasmonic Reactor]]''' — one of the best reactors in the game.

{{MessageBox
| header = ⚠ Work in Progress
| text   = Detailed Arena fight strategies, exact round composition, and reliable counter-strategies are not yet well-documented. The following is high-level guidance only.
