* The Arena features escalating fights against [[CyBulwark]] and other champion bots
* [[Lava Diamond|Lava Diamonds]] can be wagered in Arena bets to multiply your Diamond reserves (high risk, high reward)
* Complete this when your squad is well-established — ideally with multiple [[Rayden Device|Raydens]] and [[Pneumatron|Pneu Reactors]] equipped
* Target Patrol 2 or later for a reliable Arena attempt, though a strong Patrol 1 squad can attempt it

